\nconductivity zones. These findings are only based on the information content in\na single resolution-limited tomogram and extending the analysis to tracer or\nhigher resolution surface GPR data might lead to different conclusions (e.g.,\nthat discrete facies boundaries are necessary).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Jan 2017 12:31:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-09"}
